    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it\u2014not a single scratch or a speck of dust to be found anywhere. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
