    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, preserved in true collector-grade condition. This specimen features the iconic 13B-REW rotary engine, utilizing its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration to provide seamless power delivery. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the powertrain has undergone a recent specialized inspection confirming optimal compression across all rotor faces. The chassis remains factory-spec, retaining the lightweight four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for surgical handling precision. The exterior finish is flawless, highlighting the FD's timeless 'flow management' aerodynamics, while the interior remains free of the common delamination or wear found in lesser examples. This is a rare, unmodified survivor optimized for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and analog feedback.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
