    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it was brand new! It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously pampered, and the paint is still glowing. No scratches, no spills\u2014just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car smell! I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come swing by and see it for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
