    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precise six-speed Getrag manual transmission. The mechanicals are impeccable: the dual-VANOS system has been serviced to factory tolerances, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure long-term structural integrity. The chassis retains its factory-spec variable M differential lock and telepathic hydraulic steering feedback. Finished in flawless original paint with no oxidation, the interior is equally pristine, featuring Nappa leather with zero bolster wear and intact pixels on all displays. This is a mechanically sorted, investment-quality icon for the serious enthusiast.",
